#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Sissejuhatus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The TNEF File Viewer allows to handle easily mail attachments using the TNEF "
"format. Those attachments are usually found in mails coming from <trademark "
"class=\"registered\">Microsoft</trademark> mail servers and embed the mail "
"properties as well as the actual attachments."
msgstr ""
"TNEF-failide näitaja võimaldab vähese vaevaga kasutada kirjadele lisatud "
"TNEF-vormingus manuseid. Tavaliselt leiab selliseid manuseid kirjadel, mis "
"on pärit <trademark class=\"registered\">Microsoft</trademark> e-posti "
"serveritest, ning need hõlmavad nii kirja omadusi kui ka tegelikke manuseid."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An attachment in TNEF format is most often named <filename>winmail.dat</"
"filename> or <filename>win.dat</filename>."
msgstr ""
"TNEF-vormingus manus kannab enamasti nime <filename>winmail.dat</filename> "
"või <filename>win.dat</filename>."

